f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T06:14:29.000Z","msg":"視乎出版社，有啲香港作者嘅書晌台灣嘅電子書平台上面有得賣。<br />\n<br />\n例如讀墨都有少量香港作家出的書<br />\n讀墨: <a href=\"https://readmoo.com/contributor/9941\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freadmoo.com%2Fcontributor%2F9941&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruYoP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=acf66447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://readmoo.com/contributor/9941</a><br />\n<br />\n另外Google Book都會有香港出版嘅書。但我睇開學術書多(即係XX大學出版社果類), 所以都唔太清楚有無你想睇果啲。<br />\n<br />\n不過整體黎講，香港出版嘅書的確係比較少有電子版。<br />\n<br />\n我見有啲台灣人會寫信去啲台灣出版社果度問佢地出唔出電子版。如果你真係好希望佢地出，都可以試吓咁做。"},{"pid":"c5e9a35833b6cbe5af7be7f5a0f9751c142daa13","tid":1772836,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T01:09:19.000Z","msg":"好讀<br />\n呢個網有好多繁體書免費比你download"},{"pid":"8b2581370f23a491cf6c60d5dfe541c68ac7ebde","tid":1772836,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T01:12:36.000Z","msg":"博客來<br />\nKobo<br />\n香港有個叫超閱網"},{"pid":"e6ab5b15e35be2cb265cefc1c07d40e7be6f9384","tid":1772836,"uid":1482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca6700b232c6f94d1e254a5bcc69f82940ceda4d","tid":1772836,"uid":43571,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"cb970c61e54a3c79ceeeb81a399ae72910373d97","tid":1772836,"uid":300172,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"ff2d5ee7cf8613baec95e7633db6595ffbece50f","tid":1772836,"uid":43571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:55:25.000Z","msg":"想入坑睇電子書<br />\n上網睇資料見英文書就推kindle<br />\n繁中都係台灣嘅平台<br />\n想問下香港嘅書係咪通常冇出電子書/咩平台會多啲<br />\n求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T00:41:50.000Z","msg":"如果唔介意睇簡體字，<a href=\"http://可以試去Amazon.cn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%A9%A6%E5%8E%BBAmazon.cn&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruYoP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5Ssng